ZH: 地震发生在凌晨三点。
EN: An earthquake occurred at three o'clock in the early morning.

ZH: 这次地震带来了很多破坏。
EN: This earthquake brought a lot of destruction.

ZH: 我们在这次地震中幸运地逃过一劫。
EN: We were lucky to escape unharmed in this earthquake.

ZH: 地震让人们感到恐慌。
EN: Earthquakes make people feel panicked.

ZH: 震动来自地底下的地震。
EN: The shaking came from an earthquake underground.

ZH: 这个城市正在寻求建立更好的地震预警系统。
EN: This city is seeking to establish a better earthquake warning system.

ZH: 他们在地震中捐赠了大量的物资。
EN: They donated a large amount of supplies during the earthquake.

ZH: 这座建筑在地震中完全倒塌了。
EN: This building completely collapsed during the earthquake.

ZH: 大楼震动了几分钟。
EN: The building shook for several minutes.

ZH: 每年都发生数百起小型地震。
EN: Hundreds of small earthquakes occur every year.

ZH: 地震会带来巨大的损失。
EN: Earthquakes can cause significant damage.

ZH: 地震造成了大面积的停电。
EN: The earthquake resulted in widespread power outages.

ZH: 震感从脚下传来。
EN: The tremor was felt from under our feet.

ZH: 他在震后立刻报告了地震情况。
EN: He immediately reported the earthquake situation after the tremor.

ZH: 地震预警让人们有时间采取安全措施。
EN: Earthquake warnings give people time to take safety measures.

ZH: 地震调查人员正在评估损害程度。
EN: Earthquake investigators are assessing the level of damage.

ZH: 地震造成了水源受到污染。
EN: The earthquake caused contamination of the water supply.

ZH: 房屋保险通常不包括地震损害。
EN: Home insurance typically does not cover earthquake damage.

ZH: 地震警报使人们紧张不安。
EN: Earthquake alarms make people nervous.

ZH: 地震恢复需要一段时间。
EN: It takes time to recover from an earthquake.
